<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.280255>
    bibo:endPage "27" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "3222" ;
    dc:creator "Razowski, Józef; Brown, John W." ;
    dc:date "2012" ;
    dc:title "Descriptions of new Tortricidae (Lepidoptera) reared from native fruit in Kenya" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.280256>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.280258>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.280260> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.280256>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 8. Adults of Tortricidae. 1, Phtheochroa aarviki (paratype male), 2, Endothenia ator (holotype female), 3, Endothenia ator (paratype male), 4, Concinocordis wilsonarum (holotype male), 5, Anthozela psychotriae (paratype female), 6, Cosmetra podocarpivora (holotype male), 7, Cosmetra taitana (holotype male), 8, Gypsonoma scolopiae (paratype male)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/280256/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.280258>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15 – 22. Male genitalia. 15, Phtheochroa aarviki, genital capsule (GS USNM 84,907), 16, P. aarviki, phallus (GS USNM 84,907), 17, Endothenia ator (GS USNM 85,887), 18, Concinocordis wilsonarum (GS USNM 128,811), 19, Anthozela psychotriae (GS USNM 95,905), 20, Cosmetra podocarpivora (GS USNM 124,453), 21, Cosmetra taitana (GS USNM 124,442), 22, Gypsonoma scolopiae (GS USNM 128,819)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/280258/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.280260>
    dc:description "FIGURES 29 – 33. Female genitalia. 29, Phtheochroa aarviki (GS USNM 84906), 30, Endothenia ator (GS USNM 124,476), 31, Concinocordis wilsonarum (GS USNM 128,812), 32, Anthozela chrysoxantha (GS USNM 124,066), 33, Anthozela psychotriae (GS USNM 128,814)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/280260/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

